message.body: Hey! Just wanted to follow up about doing the editing! I am interested
And - do you still want my books ?
Yes and yes! I'm working on the website currently : www.bonnieonline.com
I'm raising the rates tho don't worry- just starting cheap bc I already have tons of projects and clients and a shared drop box I'll send ya
But so far it's all colleagues and friends and broke MFA students so I've been charging very little but trust me I'll charge more as soon as it's official and clients are strangers
Sounds good! I am free tues or Wednesday
I can drop books off at last drop, if you want !!

Yes sounds great- you can leave them at last drop for me. How does Wednesday at 4 sound? Or any time after 4 is great too. We can meet at Last drop too if you want. The nexus upon which the city turns
Or I guess the world turns in those emojis
Haha! Could you do later actually-- maybe like 6:30 ?
